Upstream attribution
--------------------

This project is a fork of Stephen Brennan's `lsh` teaching shell:

    https://github.com/brenns10/lsh
    http://brennan.io/2015/01/16/write-a-shell-in-c/

Stephen released the original under the Unlicense (public domain
dedication), which permits unrestricted relicensing of derivative
works. The jvmlab-lsh fork ships under 0BSD for consistency with the
rest of the jvmlab project (`jvmlab-build`, `jvmlab-toybox`), which
use the same licence. This preserves the effectively-permissive
intent of Stephen's original while matching the jvmlab-wide text.

Stephen retains authorship credit for all upstream code paths; see
the header comment in `src/main.c` for the line-by-line attribution.
